        research <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">subjects</ENAMEX> in evolutionary biology since <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">T. H.</ENAMEX>
        <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Morgan</ENAMEX> first used 
        Drosophila melanogaster as a genetic
        tool in the early part of <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">the 20th Century</TIMEX>. Polytene
