        The main objective of the present study is to place the
        chromosomal inversion data into a phylogenetic framework.
        We examine the congruence of <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">DNA</ENAMEX> sequence <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">characters</ENAMEX> and
        chromosomal inversion data in <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">four</NUMEX> different species groups
